--------- v7.0.0 ---------

+ Redesigned the main menu to be responsive and a bit prettier
+ Custom image upload now supports larger images, taking care of resizing/cropping for you
+ Ability to convert ad-hoc games of Dartzee to templates
+ 8 achievements (Chucklevision, Stylish Finish, One Hit Wonder, In Bounds, Team Wins)
+ Achievements now indicate whether they are available in individual or team games
+ Dartboards in Dartzee now indicate when missing the board is allowed
= Overhauled the achievements layout, so all the achievements now fit on one screen
= Improved performance of dartboard rendering
= Fixed excessive memory usage of dartboard rendering, which caused the app to crash occasionally
= Fixed AI speed slider location to cope with resizing games
= 93.4% test coverage (12766 / 13670 lines covered by 2373 tests)

